{"tid":50045,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"補習見得多學生，發覺大致分兩類","createTime":"2016-12-22T06:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T09:39:03.000Z","uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5763da1eb6e3dc7d293db84d98aef95c2002b338","tid":50045,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"第一種學生好怕你問佢野，佢一開始會覺得自己咩都唔識，其實我已經就住佢程度黎問，只要聽住我講書已經輕鬆諗 + 答得到，慢慢啱得多就開始建立到自信心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時候遇到難既題目，我會問下佢意見應該點落手解難，然後佢俾左個方向無論對錯我都照做，特登做錯俾佢睇等佢知點解錯，慢慢建立到對工程數學既觸覺。<br />\n<br />\n久而久之佢變成唔怕醜肯嘗試，而且答案 make sense 既學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常呢堆學生最後都升到三大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861db6962627185dcf2ab3edca84e225de4eb269","tid":50045,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"另一類呢？"},{"pid":"a8fe6c0ac31a676620c5877e35a375187c286f3e","tid":50045,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"另一種係相反，亦都係最難教既學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對自己有盲目既自信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n吸收知識既程度大家都差不多，但係呢類人做數好鐘意跳 step，連禁計數機都要用最快既方法禁，結果禁到錯哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講左十幾次要小心慢慢禁大把時間，結果次次都係懶快禁機禁錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後學完又話啲野好淺，咁我又同意真係幾淺既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜往往因爲覺得淺而輕視，mid term teat 永遠都係錯係唔小心野搞到得 7x 分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考試明明覺得佢拎到九成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟應該點教先可以幫佢改到呢個壞習慣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3ed7fb3ddeb4192990e4e737a1e81b45be6e00","tid":50045,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:05:40.000Z","msg":"感覺佢係會覺得考試早走 = 屈機果類人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時補習做早都要懶快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dcc55ff87cf75944278bdc4855ce731d57cb24","tid":50045,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"有冇補過工程妹?"},{"pid":"92c6f014bee0876c68683c7fa4a5ab09457d3d51","tid":50045,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"應該點樣幫佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62775d5410db223d7d605e896366a5434c689086","tid":50045,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇補過工程妹?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3482b0bc08662c615cee5f8943500f77a7693c84","tid":50045,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇補過工程妹?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇上床"},{"pid":"49d01680f0ce4478705c469631c737da4f31f4e6","tid":50045,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇補過工程妹?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇上床</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔搞呢啲野"},{"pid":"97dcb5d4703d44351a90887e145ca2ae64a9c65b","tid":50045,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-